comments: Gobert (UTA) delivers contact with his arm to Tatum (BOS) following the screening action.
Schroder (BOS) places his off-arm against Conley (UTA) and releases from the contact.
Horford (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Conley (UTA) and absorbs the contact.
Horford (BOS) legally contests Conley's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Conley (UTA) makes contact to Tatum's (BOS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Horford (BOS) legally contests Mitchell's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Conley (UTA) is in a legal guarding position along Schroder's (BOS) path when Schroder creates the marginal contact by extending his leg.
Horford (BOS) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Smart (BOS) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Tatum (BOS) extends his leg as Gobert (UTA) closes out. The contact is marginal.
Tatum (BOS) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
